To run the system follow these steps:
1) Download the source code 'code.zip' and extract it.
2) Change the directory to the extracted folder 'code'.
3) Run the command: python reverb_2.0.py test_tweets
   where 'test_tweets' is the file containing the test tweets from which relation has to be extracted.

Note: If you want to make changes to ReVerb and extend this tool than recompile it using steps mentioned in file "code/reverb-core-master/ReVerb_Recompile_Steps".
